== 概要 ==
{{tlx|ELL2}} is a simple template for inserting a citation to the second edition of the ''Encyclopedia of Language and Linguistics'', which is commonly cited in articles on languages and linguistics.

== 參數及使用方法 ==
*First parameter: optional author name for an entry.
*Second parameter: optional entry title.
*{{code|style{{=}}citation}}: Use {{tlx|citation}} instead of {{tlx|cite book}}.  This changes the look slightly (basically, commas instead of periods are used to separate sections of the citation), and should be used when the remaining citations use {{tlx|citation}}.  In both cases, parenthetical references inserted using {{tlx|harv}} or similar templates will work properly.
